#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:2
msgid "安全防御"
msgstr "Security Defenses"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:5
msgid "安全设计"
msgstr "Security Design"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:8
msgid "边界划分"
msgstr "Boundary Separation"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:9
msgid "大模型应用需要明确系统指令、用户输入、外部数据、模型输出和工具结果的边界。不可信内容只能作为数据处理，不能被当作指令直接执行。"
msgstr ""
"LLM applications need clear boundaries between system instructions, user "
"input, external data, model output, and tool results. Untrusted content can "
"only be processed as data and must not be directly executed as instructions."

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:12
msgid "最小权限"
msgstr "Least Privilege"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:13
msgid "模型和 Agent 调用工具时应遵循最小权限原则。不同业务场景应使用不同凭证、不同权限范围和不同网络访问策略，避免一个模型会话拥有过大的操作能力。"
msgstr ""
"Models and Agents should follow the principle of least privilege when calling "
"tools. Different business scenarios should use different credentials, "
"permission scopes, and network access policies to avoid giving a single model "
"session excessive operational capability."

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:16
msgid "显式授权"
msgstr "Explicit Authorization"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:17
msgid "对高风险操作应增加人工确认或二次授权，例如转账、删除、发送邮件、修改权限、执行代码、访问敏感数据等。确认内容应包含操作对象、影响范围和关键参数。"
msgstr ""
"High-risk operations should require human confirmation or secondary "
"authorization, such as transfers, deletions, sending email, changing "
"permissions, executing code, or accessing sensitive data. The confirmation "
"should include the operation target, scope of impact, and key parameters."

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:20
msgid "输入分级"
msgstr "Input Classification"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:21
msgid "将输入来源按可信度分级处理。用户直接输入、企业内部文档、互联网网页、邮件附件、第三方 API 返回值等应采用不同的清洗、隔离和审计策略。"
msgstr ""
"Input sources should be handled by trust level. Direct user input, internal "
"enterprise documents, Internet web pages, email attachments, and third-party "
"API responses should use different sanitization, isolation, and audit "
"strategies."

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:24
msgid "输出隔离"
msgstr "Output Isolation"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:25
msgid ""
"模型输出不应直接进入危险解释器。对 HTML、Markdown、SQL、Shell、Python、模板、JSON、YAML "
"等输出，应按下游语义进行校验、转义或沙箱执行。"
msgstr ""
"Model output should not be passed directly into dangerous interpreters. For "
"outputs such as HTML, Markdown, SQL, Shell, Python, templates, JSON, and "
"YAML, validate, escape, or execute them in a sandbox according to downstream "
"semantics."

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:28
msgid "记忆控制"
msgstr "Memory Control"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:29
msgid "长期记忆和会话记忆需要限制写入来源、写入内容和读取范围。来自不可信内容的指令不应进入长期记忆，敏感信息不应被长期保存。"
msgstr ""
"Long-term memory and session memory need restrictions on write sources, write "
"content, and read scope. Instructions from untrusted content should not enter "
"long-term memory, and sensitive information should not be stored long term."

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:32
msgid "可观测性"
msgstr "Observability"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:33
msgid "应记录模型请求、检索结果、工具调用、权限决策、拦截原因和用户确认结果。日志中需要脱敏，避免把 Token、密钥、个人信息和业务敏感数据写入日志。"
msgstr ""
"Record model requests, retrieval results, tool calls, permission decisions, "
"blocking reasons, and user confirmation results. Logs need redaction to avoid "
"writing tokens, keys, personal information, and business-sensitive data to "
"logs."

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:36
msgid "防御策略"
msgstr "Defense Strategies"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:39
msgid "提示词防护"
msgstr "Prompt Protection"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:40
msgid "系统提示词中明确区分指令和数据"
msgstr "Clearly distinguish instructions from data in system prompts"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:41
msgid "对外部内容使用引用块、标签或结构化字段包裹"
msgstr "Wrap external content in quote blocks, tags, or structured fields"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:42
msgid "降低提示词中敏感规则和密钥的暴露"
msgstr "Reduce exposure of sensitive rules and keys in prompts"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:43
msgid "避免把安全策略只放在提示词中实现"
msgstr "Avoid implementing security policies only in prompts"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:44
msgid "对高风险任务使用独立的安全判定逻辑"
msgstr "Use independent security decision logic for high-risk tasks"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:47
msgid "输入校验"
msgstr "Input Validation"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:48
msgid "限制输入长度、文件类型和文件大小"
msgstr "Limit input length, file types, and file size"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:49
msgid "对上传文件进行解析沙箱隔离"
msgstr "Parse uploaded files in sandbox isolation"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:50
msgid "对 URL、邮箱、域名、IP 等字段进行格式校验"
msgstr "Validate the format of fields such as URLs, email addresses, domains, and IPs"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:51
msgid "对来自互联网的内容增加来源标识"
msgstr "Add source labels to content from the Internet"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:52
msgid "对可疑内容进行安全分类和降权处理"
msgstr "Classify suspicious content for security and lower its weight"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:55
msgid "输出校验"
msgstr "Output Validation"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:56
msgid "使用结构化输出 Schema"
msgstr "Use structured output schemas"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:57
msgid "对工具参数进行白名单校验"
msgstr "Validate tool parameters against an allowlist"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:58
msgid "对 HTML / Markdown 进行安全渲染"
msgstr "Render HTML / Markdown safely"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:59
msgid "对代码和命令输出进行人工确认或沙箱执行"
msgstr "Require human confirmation or sandbox execution for code and command output"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:60
msgid "对敏感信息进行检测和脱敏"
msgstr "Detect and redact sensitive information"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:63
msgid "工具安全"
msgstr "Tool Security"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:64
msgid "为工具定义明确的权限边界"
msgstr "Define clear permission boundaries for tools"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:65
msgid "将只读工具和写操作工具分离"
msgstr "Separate read-only tools from write-operation tools"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:66
msgid "对高危工具启用人工确认"
msgstr "Enable human confirmation for high-risk tools"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:67
msgid "限制工具可访问的网络、文件和账号范围"
msgstr "Limit the networks, files, and accounts accessible to tools"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:68
msgid "对工具调用进行审计和限速"
msgstr "Audit and rate-limit tool calls"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:69
msgid "对工具返回值标记为不可信数据"
msgstr "Mark tool return values as untrusted data"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:72
msgid "RAG 安全"
msgstr "RAG Security"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:73
msgid "控制知识库写入权限"
msgstr "Control write permissions for knowledge bases"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:74
msgid "对文档来源进行校验和签名"
msgstr "Validate and sign document sources"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:75
msgid "对入库内容进行安全扫描"
msgstr "Security-scan content before ingestion"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:76
msgid "检索结果附带来源和时间信息"
msgstr "Attach source and time information to retrieval results"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:77
msgid "限制单个文档对最终答案的影响"
msgstr "Limit the influence of any single document on the final answer"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:78
msgid "对隐藏指令、不可见字符、混淆内容进行处理"
msgstr "Handle hidden instructions, invisible characters, and obfuscated content"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:79
msgid "定期重建索引并清理过期数据"
msgstr "Regularly rebuild indexes and clean up expired data"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:82
msgid "Agent 安全"
msgstr "Agent Security"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:83
msgid "限制最大执行步数"
msgstr "Limit the maximum number of execution steps"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:84
msgid "限制最大工具调用次数"
msgstr "Limit the maximum number of tool calls"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:85
msgid "限制单次任务预算"
msgstr "Limit the budget for a single task"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:86
msgid "对外部动作进行人工确认"
msgstr "Require human confirmation for external actions"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:87
msgid "使用任务级临时凭证"
msgstr "Use task-level temporary credentials"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:88
msgid "禁止模型自行扩大权限"
msgstr "Prevent the model from expanding its own permissions"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:89
msgid "对计划和执行结果进行审计"
msgstr "Audit plans and execution results"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:92
msgid "模型接口安全"
msgstr "Model Interface Security"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:93
msgid "对接口进行认证和鉴权"
msgstr "Authenticate and authorize interfaces"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:94
msgid "对用户、租户、模型和场景进行限速"
msgstr "Rate-limit by user, tenant, model, and scenario"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:95
msgid "设置 Token、并发、费用和时间上限"
msgstr "Set limits on tokens, concurrency, cost, and time"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:96
msgid "对异常请求进行熔断"
msgstr "Apply circuit breaking to abnormal requests"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:97
msgid "对模型版本和参数进行变更管理"
msgstr "Manage changes to model versions and parameters"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:98
msgid "避免在客户端暴露模型密钥"
msgstr "Avoid exposing model keys on the client side"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:101
msgid "数据安全"
msgstr "Data Security"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:102
msgid "训练和微调数据应进行分级分类"
msgstr "Classify training and fine-tuning data by level and category"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:103
msgid "敏感数据进入模型前应脱敏或最小化"
msgstr "Desensitize or minimize sensitive data before it enters the model"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:104
msgid "日志、缓存、向量索引应设置访问控制"
msgstr "Set access controls on logs, caches, and vector indexes"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:105
msgid "用户数据应按租户隔离"
msgstr "Isolate user data by tenant"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:106
msgid "数据删除和模型记忆删除应有明确流程"
msgstr "Define clear processes for data deletion and model memory deletion"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:107
msgid "第三方模型调用应评估数据出境和合规要求"
msgstr ""
"Evaluate cross-border data transfer and compliance requirements for calls to "
"third-party models"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:110
msgid "安全基线"
msgstr "Security Baseline"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:111
msgid "大模型接口必须有认证、鉴权和限速"
msgstr "LLM interfaces must have authentication, authorization, and rate limiting"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:112
msgid "不可信内容必须标记来源，不能作为系统指令执行"
msgstr "Untrusted content must be labeled with its source and must not be executed as system instructions"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:113
msgid "模型输出进入下游组件前必须校验"
msgstr "Model output must be validated before entering downstream components"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:114
msgid "高危工具调用必须有权限控制和人工确认"
msgstr "High-risk tool calls must have permission control and human confirmation"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:115
msgid "RAG 知识库必须控制写入权限和文档来源"
msgstr "RAG knowledge bases must control write permissions and document sources"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:116
msgid "Agent 必须限制执行步数、预算和权限范围"
msgstr "Agents must limit execution steps, budgets, and permission scope"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:117
msgid "日志、缓存、向量库必须脱敏和访问控制"
msgstr "Logs, caches, and vector databases must be redacted and access-controlled"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:118
msgid "模型、提示词、工具、知识库变更必须可审计"
msgstr "Changes to models, prompts, tools, and knowledge bases must be auditable"

#: ../../source/llm/defense.rst:119
msgid "应定期进行红队测试和回归测试"
msgstr "Red-team testing and regression testing should be performed regularly"
